        <abstract>
            <p>Bernhard Studer has been at Down. Studer will not be able to join HDelaB’s Ordnance Survey working party.</p>
            <p>CD is glad to hear about very old rocks under Silurians. "There is something grand and mysterious at these depths."</p>
